    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>基于Hexo搭建个人博客（三）</title>
      <link href="/2023/02/03/hexo3/"/>
      <url>/2023/02/03/hexo3/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h1 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h1><p>由于博客美化的功能散布在各个网页中，不好找<br>所以本系列文案主要是整合性质<br>此外会把原文章地址粘贴在相关页旁</p><h1 id="标签页"><a href="#标签页" class="headerlink" title="标签页"></a>标签页</h1><p>前往你的Hexo博客根目录，打开cmd命令窗口执行<strong>hexo new page tags</strong>。<br>在 博客根目录的<strong>source</strong>文件夹下会生成一个含有<strong>index.md</strong>文件的<strong>tags</strong>文件夹。<br>修改这个<strong>index.md</strong>，添加<strong>type: “tags”</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: 标签</span><br><span class="line">date: 2022-12-23 12:34:12</span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;tags&quot;</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="分类页"><a href="#分类页" class="headerlink" title="分类页"></a>分类页</h1><p>前往你的Hexo博客根目录，打开cmd命令窗口执行<strong>hexo new page categories</strong>。<br>在 博客根目录的<strong>source</strong>文件夹下会生成一个含有<strong>index.md</strong>文件的<strong>categories</strong>文件夹。<br>修改这个<strong>index.md</strong>，添加<strong>type: “categories”</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: 分类</span><br><span class="line">date: 2022-12-23 12:34:12</span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;categories&quot;</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="友情链接"><a href="#友情链接" class="headerlink" title="友情链接"></a>友情链接</h1><p>前往你的Hexo博客根目录，打开cmd命令窗口执行<strong>hexo new page link</strong>。<br>在 博客根目录的<strong>source</strong>文件夹下会生成一个含有<strong>index.md</strong>文件的<strong>link</strong>文件夹。<br>修改这个<strong>index.md</strong>，添加<strong>type: “link”</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: 友链</span><br><span class="line">date: 2022-12-23 12:34:12</span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;link&quot;</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="友链信息"><a href="#友链信息" class="headerlink" title="友链信息"></a>友链信息</h2><p>前往博客根目录的<strong>source&#x2F;_data</strong>创建一个文件<strong>link.yml</strong>（如果沒有 _data 文件夹，请自行创建）<br>写入如下内容（可以自行更改）</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">- class_name: 友情链接</span><br><span class="line">  class_desc: 那些人，那些事</span><br><span class="line">  link_list:</span><br><span class="line">    - name: 唐志远の博客</span><br><span class="line">      link: https://tzy1997.com/</span><br><span class="line">      avatar: https://bu.dusays.com/2022/01/14/cd5ffd485f867.jpg</span><br><span class="line">      descr: 古今之成大事者，不惟有超世之才，亦必有坚忍不拔之志。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="404界面"><a href="#404界面" class="headerlink" title="404界面"></a>404界面</h1><p>在 博客根目录的 <strong>_config.yml</strong> 找到 <strong>error_404</strong>（ctrl+f查找内容）<br>可以自行修改</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">error_404:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  subtitle: &#x27;Page Not Found&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">  background: /immm/404.jpg </span><br><span class="line"># 我这里直接放了张图</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="如需本地预览，请访问-http-localhost-4000-404-html"><a href="#如需本地预览，请访问-http-localhost-4000-404-html" class="headerlink" title="如需本地预览，请访问 http://localhost:4000/404.html"></a>如需本地预览，请访问 <a href="http://localhost:4000/404.html">http://localhost:4000/404.html</a></h2><h1 id="参考"><a href="#参考" class="headerlink" title="参考"></a>参考</h1><p><a href="https://tzy1997.com/articles/hexo1603/">唐志远の博客</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> Hexo </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
